7748466.review:
Due to its slow start, I kind of relegated this game to the backlog. After a few months I had nothing else to play and started it again. As soon as I left the first chapter, it stopped being tedious and started to grow on me. I could not stop playing it anymore. 
The only things I would comment are:
- slow start;
- slow animation (player);
- not state of art 3d.
If none of the above are gamebreakers to you (they were not gamebreakers for me), you will enjoy this game.
